before this senate is clear,

01:45:21.908 --> 01:45:25.642
it is thoughtful,
and above all, it is brave.

01:45:26.542 --> 01:45:28.408
This resolution is
in three parts.

01:45:28.974 --> 01:45:30.873
After I read out each one,

01:45:30.875 --> 01:45:33.275
I will call the senate members
up to cast their votes.

01:45:34.041 --> 01:45:37.740
Each part requires
a two-thirds majority to pass.

01:45:37.742 --> 01:45:39.443
That's eight votes.

01:45:40.974 --> 01:45:42.108
Part one.

01:45:43.108 --> 01:45:45.574
Two students,
one black, one white,

01:45:45.576 --> 01:45:49.443
to be appointed every year
to the Durham school board.

01:45:49.742 --> 01:45:51.742
I vote yes.

01:45:55.242 --> 01:45:56.409
Mr. Watford.

01:45:58.176 --> 01:45:59.376
I'm a no.

01:46:01.543 --> 01:46:03.240
I vote yes.

01:46:03.242 --> 01:46:05.709
Part one passes
with eight votes.

01:46:08.743 --> 01:46:14.375
Part two. This calls that summer classes
be included in the school board budget

01:46:14.377 --> 01:46:17.442
so the black students become
level with their white peers.

01:46:17.444 --> 01:46:18.577
Mr. Weeks.

01:46:20.277 --> 01:46:22.575
I vote no.

01:46:22.577 --> 01:46:23.644
Mr. Cox.

01:46:24.676 --> 01:46:25.810
I vote yes.

01:46:28.210 --> 01:46:29.277
I vote yes.

01:46:32.877 --> 01:46:35.177
Part two passes
with eight votes.

01:46:46.976 --> 01:46:48.144
Part three.

01:46:52.378 --> 01:46:53.977
Public school integration.

01:46:55.545 --> 01:46:56.677
In summary,

01:46:57.578 --> 01:47:00.443
this calls for full
and immediate integration

01:47:00.445 --> 01:47:03.378
starting in the fall semester
of this school year.

01:47:04.244 --> 01:47:08.242
The resolution defines full
integration by setting a race ratio

01:47:08.244 --> 01:47:13.077
of no less than 25 percent
of any race at each school.

01:47:13.878 --> 01:47:17.343
And further, that busing be
made available to students

01:47:17.345 --> 01:47:20.645
to aid in the implementation
of this ratio.

01:47:23.045 --> 01:47:25.778
We'll start the vote
on this side with Miss Wilson.

01:47:35.446 --> 01:47:37.279
I vote yes.

01:47:42.813 --> 01:47:43.913
Mr. Watford?

01:47:50.447 --> 01:47:51.413
I vote no.

01:47:55.813 --> 01:47:57.480
Mr. Mose.

01:48:01.747 --> 01:48:03.246
I vote yes.

01:48:08.246 --> 01:48:09.413
Mr. Weeks.

01:48:13.914 --> 01:48:16.979
I vote "hell no."

01:48:23.347 --> 01:48:24.613
Mr. Cox?

01:48:29.514 --> 01:48:31.014
I vote "hell yes."

01:48:39.581 --> 01:48:40.748
Mr. Trombley.

01:48:51.980 --> 01:48:53.515
Thank you, Mr. Riddick.

01:49:00.782 --> 01:49:03.581
I believe in school
integration, and I vote yes.

01:49:08.682 --> 01:49:10.115
