Miss Atwater.

01:59:26.435 --> 01:59:28.202
Yeah. Hello?

02:00:23.437 --> 02:00:24.837
Okay, Mr. Ellis.

02:00:26.969 --> 02:00:28.103
How many?

02:00:28.471 --> 02:00:31.304
Well, you lost
about 650 gallons.

02:00:32.037 --> 02:00:33.737
You're lucky
the thing didn't explode.

02:00:34.270 --> 02:00:35.771
Yeah, okay.

02:00:36.270 --> 02:00:39.904
You want to replace the loss?
