02:00:42.437 --> 02:00:44.570
No. Let's see how
the rest of the month goes.

02:00:44.572 --> 02:00:45.638
All right.

02:00:46.970 --> 02:00:49.472
What's this?
Would you sign both pages?

02:01:11.805 --> 02:01:12.939
Thank you, Mr. Ellis.

02:01:13.673 --> 02:01:15.171
Change your mind,
give us a call.

02:01:37.873 --> 02:01:39.606
Mr. Ellis.
Mm-hmm?

02:01:41.139 --> 02:01:43.139
If you need to let me go,
it's okay.

02:01:43.806 --> 02:01:45.906
You know,
until things pick up again.

02:01:47.439 --> 02:01:50.306
I appreciate that, Jeb.
But we're not there yet, okay?

02:01:50.740 --> 02:01:53.340
So for now, go ahead,
take your lunch break.

02:01:54.474 --> 02:01:56.105
Okay, Mr. Ellis.

02:01:56.873 --> 02:01:57.940
All right.

02:02:24.274 --> 02:02:28.104
I hope you didn't come here to
ask me to co-chair somethin' else.

02:02:28.106 --> 02:02:30.905
Nah. I just came
to say good-bye is all.

02:02:30.907 --> 02:02:33.675
Back to Raleigh, huh?
Back to Raleigh.

02:02:41.508 --> 02:02:43.106
What trouble you been causin'?

02:02:43.108 --> 02:02:45.707
Just organizing, you know me.

02:02:46.408 --> 02:02:48.807
It's what you do, right?
It's just what I do.

02:02:49.176 --> 02:02:50.906
I sure wish
you coulda been there

02:02:50.908 --> 02:02:53.473
when we handed in
our resolution. Mmm.

02:02:53.475 --> 02:02:55.707
Old Carvie Oldham
didn't even show up.

02:02:58.808 --> 02:03:00.276
Wish I'd seen that.

02:03:00.775 --> 02:03:02.142
How are you doin', C.P.?

02:03:03.009 --> 02:03:04.842
Oh, had a little trouble here.

02:03:06.009 --> 02:03:07.973
Just trying to
put it back together.

02:03:07.975 --> 02:03:09.342
Yeah, we heard.

02:03:10.375 --> 02:03:12.140
I'm so sorry, C.P.

02:03:12.142 --> 02:03:15.009
It's okay.
Although not sure it matters much.

02:03:15.775 --> 02:03:18.842
Nobody stoppin' to buy gas
from me these days.

02:03:21.277 --> 02:03:24.675
Well... Maybe things
will pick up for you.

02:03:26.442 --> 02:03:28.010
What you smilin' at?

02:04:00.011 --> 02:04:02.111
That's just what I do, C.P.

02:04:02.477 --> 02:04:04.744
You know that.
That's just what I do.

02:04:21.645 --> 02:04:24.744
Hey, Jeb. We got customers.

02:04:28.978 --> 02:04:31.645
Gas?

02:04:32.012 --> 02:04:33.643
- Gas?
