02:04:33.645 --> 02:04:35.210
You want gas?

02:04:35.212 --> 02:04:37.012
- Yeah, no problem.
- All right.

02:04:55.479 --> 02:04:59.443
She can upset the world with
her mouth if she wants to.

02:04:59.445 --> 02:05:02.410
But everywhere I go,
every time I pick up a newspaper,

02:05:02.412 --> 02:05:05.744
Ann Atwater's been before the
council, the county commission,

02:05:05.746 --> 02:05:08.144
or she was at some
shopping center boycotting,

02:05:08.146 --> 02:05:09.913
or she was downtown
at Woolworths.

02:05:10.480 --> 02:05:12.444
And he was woofin'
and goin' on,

02:05:12.446 --> 02:05:14.545
and the place was packed
with Klansmen.

02:05:14.547 --> 02:05:18.046
This particular night, C.P.
was up raging and ranting.

02:05:18.647 --> 02:05:20.712
That's when
I wanted to cut his head off.

02:05:20.979 --> 02:05:22.944
And after that first meeting,

02:05:22.946 --> 02:05:25.446
I actually went home saying,
this is crazy.

02:05:25.746 --> 02:05:29.645
This is absolutely crazy.
I don't think I wanna do this.

02:05:29.647 --> 02:05:32.513
I mean, I can make a living
easier than this.

02:05:39.680 --> 02:05:42.614
The story was picked up
in <i>The Washington Post.</i>

02:05:43.313 --> 02:05:45.880
"Black man calls Klansman
'brother.'"

02:05:46.481 --> 02:05:50.614
And of course, my father, when he read
the story in <i>The Washington Post...</i>

02:05:51.680 --> 02:05:53.548
he thought I had lost my mind.

02:06:01.081 --> 02:06:06.948
In becoming my friend,
C.P. has lost a lot.

02:06:07.281 --> 02:06:10.649
Look, you do not make those changes
without having to pay for 'em.

02:06:11.048 --> 02:06:13.946
I know damn well, you know.

02:06:13.948 --> 02:06:15.681
You have to pay for it
eventually.

02:06:16.315 --> 02:06:18.979
We bonded,
and we are still bonding.

02:06:18.981 --> 02:06:20.879
Until I get mad with him
at times.

02:06:20.881 --> 02:06:24.779
But we've made it through these
years, together 30 years,

02:06:24.781 --> 02:06:26.382
and we're still friends.

02:06:47.650 --> 02:06:52.449
'Cause there are C.P. Ellises and Ann
Atwaters in almost every community.

02:06:53.682 --> 02:06:55.550
